N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4207.26 - Information for commission, State Tax Department

State Regulations

Racing associations shall promptly give to the commission
and to the State Tax Department such information in writing as either may
request from time to time and shall freely and fully cooperate with them in
every way. Notes
